  app-admin/testdisk-7.0: Re-enable ext2fs

  20 Apr 2015; Nicolas Bock <nicolasbock@gentoo.org>
  +files/install-gentoo.patch, testdisk-7.0.ebuild:
  app-admin/testdisk-0.7: Fixed QA issue.  The Makefile.am had a customized
  install-data-hook which didn't conform to QA. I added a patch that changes how
  the data files are installed.

